{"tid":2282243,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[20191112] 中大二號橋無間斷催淚彈及橡膠彈　城大指揮官下令瞄頭直射","createTime":"2020-11-11T17:04:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-12T14:45:34.000Z","uid":240362,"like":28,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"b028ceb2f571eec39150ec79dada51756b62ff05","tid":2282243,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T17:04:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent-hkt1-2.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/76988602_858491351232536_6724907617090535424_n.jpg?_nc_cat=102&amp;ccb=2&amp;_nc_sid=0debeb&amp;_nc_ohc=BGvqWG7TEsUAX9GnPmW&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkt1-2.xx&amp;oh=d60f33c7e136003ad2901da1e9534f96&amp;oe=5FD24C01\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkt1-2.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F76988602_858491351232536_6724907617090535424_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D102%26ccb%3D2%26_nc_sid%3D0debeb%26_nc_ohc%3DBGvqWG7TEsUAX9GnPmW%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkt1-2.xx%26oh%3Dd60f33c7e136003ad2901da1e9534f96%26oe%3D5FD24C01&h=46246227&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n警方第二日連闖多間大學，中大校園成為主要襲擊目標，全校陷入硝煙。戰役由早上開始，中大學生為守護校園，在二號橋築起路障防線，警方狂放催淚彈及橡膠子彈，欲攻入校園拉人，中大校長段崇智及教職員數度斡旋不果，警方更三度反口，聲稱停火後突進攻。防暴警全日在校園狂轟逾千枚催淚彈，又瞄準示威者頭部發射橡膠子彈，一片混亂，多名學生及示威者受傷，有學生懷疑頭部中彈倒地，失去意識，現場要設臨時救護站救治約60名傷者，有中大生更聲稱若警方強攻入校園會自焚明志。至晚上10時，警方撤離後，戰事才稍平靜。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20191113/ENYII43TF42JPDVRJAF72KV7KY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191113%2FENYII43TF42JPDVRJAF72KV7KY%2F&d=J6hOlXozLSF63%2FYIn%2B2Auy1yjuEIKew%2F2lwpseS6mRM%3D&h=5fff0b9d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191113%2FENYII43TF42JPDVRJAF72KV7KY%2F&h=c29c24b2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20191113/ENYII43TF42JPDVRJAF72KV7KY/</a>"},{"pid":"757ece691cc72d91480ed2bf5881ddf689e7b70d","tid":2282243,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T17:04:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c48e0871a6820c2dbb05c9cde02f09437b877311","tid":2282243,"uid":240362,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T17:04:41.000Z","msg":"一批示威者在香港城市大學對開歌和老街設置路障，警方清理路障後發射數枚催淚彈至學生宿舍範圍，有學生在天橋舉傘陣與警對峙，雙方對峙期間，有示威者從傘陣伸出頭來，指揮官竟開咪向警員下指令：「佢伸個頭出嚟，就打頭啦！」警員隨即向天橋發射一發懷疑橡膠子彈，射跌一把雨傘。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20191113/TNI2AQBFCNVPWIZ3IGXCWE2NW4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191113%2FTNI2AQBFCNVPWIZ3IGXCWE2NW4%2F&d=J6hOlXozLSF63%2FYIn%2B2Auy1yjuEIKew%2F2lwpseS6mRM%3D&h=37e2f801\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191113%2FTNI2AQBFCNVPWIZ3IGXCWE2NW4%2F&h=dcdd0fc0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20191113/TNI2AQBFCNVPWIZ3IGXCWE2NW4/</a>"},{"pid":"e34b9cb2d0fdb7cc85746004cccf922433085679","tid":2282243,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T17:05:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/darkness.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/darkness.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/darkness.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"337f15d77a68301a85fdfc5c22c451c3ace34e85","tid":2282243,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T17:06:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4434cb0b33a837dded3ea8dc08d24a72d61f180e","tid":2282243,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"337f15d77a68301a85fdfc5c22c451c3ace34e85","tid":2282243,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T17:06:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs